casebody.data:
No. 13,

Original.

Texas v. New Jersey et al. [For earlier orders herein, see 369 U. S. 869; 370 U. S. 929; 371 U. S. 873; 372 U. S. 926, 973.]

The Report of the Special Master submitted in response to the order of this Court dated February 25,1963, 372 U. S. 926, is received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, with supporting briefs, to the Report of the Special Master may be filed by the parties on or before February 15, 1964. Reply briefs, if any, to such exceptions may be filed on or before March 15, 1964.
